      "type": "thought",
      "text": "The user has a BSOD with \"WHEA_UNCORRECTABLE_ERROR\" and wants me to investigate using enterprise root cause analysis, determine fixability score using \"ifix\", check reliability, and assess whether they can spend time improving PC temperature. They also want to use PowerShell and Python tools to ensure they work.\n\nFirst, I need to understand what \"ifix\" refers to. It might be a tool or a metric. Let's search for WHEA_UNCORRECTABLE_ERROR and its causes. I'll use web search.",
