      "code": "{\"query\": \"ifix fixibility score hardware\"}",
      "output": "{\n  \"search_id\": \"search_abe6189f587a423d952c34a8c4893771\",\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://lifestyle.sustainability-directory.com/learn/what-is-the-ifixit-repairability-score-and-how-is-it-calculated/\",\n      \"title\": \"What Is the “Ifixit Repairability Score” and How Is It ...\",\n      \"publish_date\": \"2025-11-15\",\n      \"excerpts\": [\n        \"Search\\n\\nClose Search\\n\\nLearn\\n\\n# What Is the “Ifixit Repairability Score” and How Is It Calculated?\\n\\nA 1-10 rating based on teardown assessment of opening difficulty, fastener type, component modularity, and parts/manual availability.\\n\\nSustainability Directory Sustainability Directory 15\\\\.11.25 1 min\\n\\n## What Is the “Ifixit Repairability Score” and How Is It Calculated?\\n\\nThe iFixit Repairability Score is a 1 to 10 rating (10 being easiest to repair) based on a product's teardown and assessment. It considers factors like the difficulty of opening the device, the use of proprietary fasteners, the modularity of components, and the availability of spare parts and repair manuals.\\n\\nIt serves as a key consumer-facing metric for product sustainability.\\n\\nWhat Is the ‘Total Cost of Ownership’ (TCO) and How Is It Calculated?\\n\\nHow Is the Water Usage Effectiveness (WUE) Metric Calculated?\\n\\nHow Does Inflation Affect the ‘Enough’ Number Calculation?\\nHow Is the PUE Metric Calculated, and What Does Each Component Represent?\\n\\nHow Can the “Care Score” Be Transparently Calculated Using IoT Data and Return Inspection?\\n\\nWhat Is the “Digital Carbon Footprint” and How Is It Calculated for an Average User?\\n\\nHow Is the Embodied Carbon of a Product Calculated across Its Lifecycle?\\n\\nWhat Is a ‘Repairability Index’ and How Is It Calculated?\\n\\nDedicated Glossaries\\n\\n## Sustainability Satellites\\n\\nJust as satellites orbit the Earth, providing a focused and detailed view of specific regions, our “Sustainability Satellites” offer an in-depth exploration of the [Sustainability Directory](https://sustainability-directory.com/) . Each satellite represents a vital aspect of this broader field, and each is presented as a domain. Glossaries illuminate the key concepts, terminology, and challenges within each area, allowing to build a more complete and nuanced understanding of the interconnected world.\\n\\n[Fashion](https://fashion.\\nsustainability-directory.com/) Lifestyle [Pollution](https://pollution.sustainability-directory.com/) [Product](https://product.sustainability-directory.com/) [Prism](https://prism.sustainability-directory.com/) [ESG](https://esg.sustainability-directory.com/) [Energy](https://energy.sustainability-directory.com/) [Climate](https://climate.sustainability-directory.com/)\\n\\n## Sustainability Directory\\n\\nA network of focused glossaries — each domain, an in-depth view.\\n\\n## Mission\\n\\nDriven by three principles: Aspire, Adapt, Amplify.\\n\\n## Approach\\n\\nDemocratising knowledge, empowering action, building space for collective impact.\\n\\n## Explore\\n\\n[Founders](https://sustainability-directory.com/expertise/founders/) [Purpose](https://sustainability-directory.com/expertise/purpose/) [Services](https://sustainability-directory.com/expertise/services/) [Contact](https://sustainability-directory.com/contact/)\\n\\n[© CC BY 4.0](https://sustainability-directory.com/expertise/reuse/)\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://nojokefna.github.io/ifixit-repair-score-site/\",\n      \"title\": \"iFixit Repairability Scores — Dashboard\",\n      \"publish_date\": null,\n      \"excerpts\": [\n        \"# iFixit Repairability Scores\\n\\nDashboard Edition\\n\\nThe officially unofficial listing of iFixit's\\nrepairability scores.\\n\\nInspired by [xiongchiamiov's GitHub](https://github.com/xiongchiamiov/ifixit-repairability-scores/) and [the original webpage](https://changedmy.name/ifixit-repairability-scores/) .\\nRewritten with latest data.\\n\\nInteractive dashboard for iFixit repairability — explore charts, search/sort/filter devices, and\\ninspect teardown links labeled Featured, Community, and Archived.  \\n[View source code on GitHub](https://github.com/NoJokeFNA/ifixit-repair-score-site/)\\n\\n## Score Distribution\\n\\nThe Repairability Score ranges from 0 to 10 — 10 = very repairable, 0 = very hard to repair.\\nIt is based on the “Repairability Scoring Rubric.” Versions 1.0 through 2.1 exist (2.1 is\\nthe latest).\\nOlder devices may have been scored with earlier rubrics and are not always directly\\ncomparable to v2.1.  \\n[See the current rubric (v2.1)](https://www.ifixit.com/Wiki/Repairability_Scoring_Rubric_v2.\\n1)\\n\\nShow Rubric\\n\\nHistogram of device repairability scores (0–10). Y-axis:\\ndevice count.\\n\\nFailed to load chart\\n\\n|Criteria |\\n| --- |\\n\\nFailed to load rubric data\\n\\n## Device Details\\n\\nTags\\n\\n* Featured\\n  \\n  Featured Guide — This guide has been found to be exceptionally cool by the\\n  iFixit staff.\\n* Community\\n  \\n  Community-Contributed Guide — An awesome member of our community made this\\n  guide. It was not created by iFixit staff.\\n* Archived\\n  \\n  Archived Guide — This guide is retained solely for historical purposes. Use\\n  the updated version of the guide to perform your repair.\\n\\nDifficulty Levels\\n\\n* Very Difficult\\n  \\n  Requires disassembling almost all of the device. Not recommended for\\n  non-professionals.\\n* Difficult\\n  \\n  Requires significant disassembly and repair knowledge.\\n* Moderate\\n  \\n  Requires some disassembly, additional tools, and basic repair\\n  knowledge.\\n* Easy\\n  \\n  Requires minimal disassembly, requires only Phillips or flat-head\\n  screwdriver.\\n* Very Easy\\nDoes not require opening device.\\n\\nAll manufacturers\\n\\nScored only All devices\\n\\nExport ▾ Density:\\nCompact Reset Theme\\n\\n|Select |Device |Teardown |Manufacturer |Score |Score (France) Beta |Scoring Rubric |\\n| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |\\n|Loading... |\\n\\n0 selected Compare Clear\\n\\nData from iFixit API · Built with Tailwind + Chart.js · Version 0.0.11\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://ifixesdevicerepair.com/\",\n      \"title\": \"Places to Get Phone Screen Fixed - IFIXES DEVICE REPAIR\",\n      \"publish_date\": null,\n      \"excerpts\": [\n        \"(806) 213-0081\\n\\n(806) 213-0081\\n\\n \\n\\n* \\n* \\n* * * *\\n* Bookings\\n* My Account\\n\\n* Signed in as:\\n* filler@godaddy.com\\n* * * *\\n* Bookings\\n* My Account\\n* Sign out\\n\\nSigned in as:\\n\\nfiller@godaddy.com\\n\\nAccount\\n\\n* * * *\\n* Bookings\\n* My Account\\n* Sign out\\n\\n* * * *\\n* \\n* Bookings\\n* My Account\\n\\n# cell phone, tablet repair best place to get phone -Tablet screen fixed\\n\\ncell phone, tablet repair best place to get phone -Tablet screen fixed cell phone, tablet repair best place to get phone -Tablet screen fixed cell phone, tablet repair best place to get phone -Tablet screen fixed\\n\\nBook Online\\n\\n#### Same Day Repairs On Most iPhone Screen Replacements\\n\\nSame Day Screen Repairs On Most iPhone 6 - iPhone 16 Pro Max. Tablet repair Computer Repair\\n\\n#### Affordable Repairs and Accessories\\n\\nCome see us here at IDR Device Repair Plainview for fast and affordable prices on repairs and accessories. If some of our prices are higher than others, we will price match.\\nWe offer our 10% discount to Teachers, Officers, First Responders, College Students, Nurses, Military, Senior Citizens.\\n\\n#### High-Quality Parts\\n\\nParts Come With A 90 Day Warranty Against Product Defect. Warranty Void If Cracked Or Liquid Damaged.\\n\\nAbout Us\\n\\nIfixes Device Repair since late 2020, repairing devices in Plainview and surrounding areas since 2010, locally owned and family owned. We offer high quality repairs at an affordable price, always with our customers in mind.\\n\\n## Services\\n\\n### Iphone Screen, Battery, Camera, Charging Port, Back Housing, Speaker Repair\\n\\nMost Repairs Done Within 30 minutes. Samsung and Other Brand parts will have to be ordered.\\n\\n* * *\\n\\n### Computer Repair\\n\\nTroubleshooting, Windows reinstalls, Data Recovery, Diagnose, Virus Removal, Battery Replacements, Custom PC Builds and More\\n\\n* * *\\n\\n### Gaming Console Repairs\\n\\nXbox, Playstation, Nintendo\\n\\n## Social\\n\\n[](https://www.facebook.com/iFixescellphonerepair/) [](https://www.tiktok.\\ncom/@ifixesdevicerepair) [](https://www.yelp.com/biz/lxTpCscbiP34Y49c8msXKw)\\n\\n## Contact Us\\n\\n#### Book an Appointment\\n\\nIFIXES DEVICE REPAIR\\\\*\\n\\nEmail\\\\*\\n\\nAttach Files\\n\\nAttachments (0)\\n\\nSend\\n\\nThis site is protected by reCAPTCHA and the Google [Privacy Policy](https://policies.google.com/privacy) and [Terms of Service](https://policies.google.com/terms) apply.\\n\\n#### IFIXES DEVICE REPAIR\\n\\n2311 West 5th Street, Plainview, Texas 79072, United States\\n\\nCall : (806) 213-0081 Text Only : (806) 572-2950\\n\\n#### Hours\\n\\n|Mon |10:00 am – 02:00 pm |\\n| --- | --- |\\n|Tue |10:00 am – 05:00 pm |\\n|Wed |10:00 am – 04:00 pm |\\n|Thu |10:00 am – 04:00 pm |\\n|Fri |10:00 am – 05:00 pm |\\n|Sat |10:00 am – 02:00 pm |\\n|Sun |Closed |\\n\\nGet directions\\n\\n## Reviews\\n\\nIFIXES DEVICE REPAIR\\n\\n2311 West 5th Street, Plainview, Texas 79072, United States\\n\\n(806) 572-2950\\n\\nPowered by\\n\\n[](https://www.godaddy.com/websites/website-builder?isc=pwugc&utm_source=wsb&utm_medium=applications&utm_campaign=en-us_corp_applications_base)\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://ifix-nyc.com/\",\n      \"title\": \"iFIX NYC | Fast Device Repair in NYC – Phones, Laptops & Consoles\",\n      \"publish_date\": null,\n      \"excerpts\": [\n        \"Virus and malware removal services – Protect your PC, laptop, or phone from security threats in NYC.\\n\\n#### Virus/Malware Removal\\n\\nRemove malware, viruses, and spyware with iFIX NYC’s expert virus removal and security services.\\n\\n[](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hHd4dgYXXP0)\\n\\nOur Experts\\n\\n## Trust our experts for reliable gadget repairs\\n\\nAt iFIX NYC, our skilled technicians provide expert gadget repair services with precision and care. With years of hands-on experience, we diagnose and fix complex issues across smartphones, tablets, laptops, and gaming consoles. Whether it’s a cracked screen, battery replacement, or hardware malfunction, our professionals ensure fast, high-quality repairs to restore your device’s performance. Trust iFIX NYC for reliable, efficient, and expert device repair solutions tailored to your needs.\\n\\nBook a Repair\\n\\nTestimonials\\n\\n## Our Happy Customers\\n\\nVisit Us\\n\\n## Find Our Repair Center in Brooklyn\\nWe are conveniently located at **1354 Broadway, Brooklyn, NY 11221** . Stop by for expert device repairs, including phones, laptops, and gaming consoles.\\nWe offer same-day service for most repairs!\\n\\n[Get Directions](https://www.google.com/maps/place/iFIX+NYC/@40.689701,-73.922672,15z/data=!4m6!3m5!1s0x89c25c12f5383863:0xde679ce82df9332c!8m2!3d40.6897011!4d-73.9226719!16s%2Fg%2F11f2w63765?hl=en&entry=ttu&g_ep=EgoyMDI1MDIwNS4xIKXMDSoASAFQAw%3D%3D)\\n\\n[](https://www.google.com/maps/place/1354+Broadway,+Brooklyn,+NY+11221)\\n\\nQuestions\\n\\n## Frequently asked questions\\n\\nWhat types of gadgets do you service?\\n\\nWe repair a wide range of electronic devices, including smartphones, tablets, laptops, desktops, and gaming consoles. Whether it’s a cracked screen, battery issue, or software problem, our expert technicians ensure top-quality repairs.\\n\\nWhat brands do you repair?\\n\\nWe specialize in repairing top brands like Apple, Samsung, Dell, HP, Lenovo, Microsoft, Sony, Asus, Acer, and more.\\nOur skilled professionals handle everything from screen replacements to hardware upgrades for leading manufacturers.\\n\\nDo you offer a warranty on your repairs?\\n\\nYes, we provide a 14-days warranty on all our repair services. This guarantees quality workmanship and ensures your device functions optimally. If any issues arise within the warranty period, we’ll fix them at no additional cost.\\n\\nHow do I get my gadget repaired?\\n\\nGetting your device repaired is easy! Visit our repair center, schedule a pickup service, or mail in your device for a fast and professional fix. Contact us to choose the most convenient repair option for you.\\n\\nDo I need to back up my data before repair?\\n\\nYes, we recommend backing up your data before repair to prevent any loss. While we take the utmost care during repairs, it’s always best to have a backup of important files and personal data.\\n\\nHow long will the repair take?\\n\\nRepair time varies based on the issue.\\nMost common fixes like screen replacements and battery swaps take 1-2 hours, while complex repairs may require 1-3 days. Contact us for an exact repair estimate for your device.\\n\\nCommon gadget repair questions answered – iFIX NYC’s expert solutions for phone, tablet, and laptop issues.\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://ifixny.com/\",\n      \"title\": \"iFIX New York® - Your Home for Electronics Repair in New York City\",\n      \"publish_date\": \"2023-11-13\",\n      \"excerpts\": [\n        \"com/iphone-repair-nyc.html)\\n\\nWe fix everything from iPhone screen repair, iPhone battery replacement, iPhone water damage to full iPhone refurbishment\\n\\n[Samsung Galaxy Repair](https://ifixny.com/samsung-galaxy-repair-nyc.html)\\n\\nRepairs for Samsung screens, Samsung battery replacement, Samsung Galaxy water damage to full refurbishment\\n\\n[Tablet Repair](https://ifixny.com/tablet-repair-nyc.html)\\n\\niPad screen repair, iPad battery replacement, iPad headphone jack repairs, water damage to full iPad refurbishment\\n\\n[Computer Repair](https://ifixny.com/computer-repair-nyc.html)\\n\\nWe repair broken laptop screens, bad power plugs, faulty laptop LCDs, broken laptop keyboards, laptop motherboards & more…\\n\\n### State-of-the-art electronics repair in NYC\\n\\niFIX New York can efficiently and effectively troubleshoot and repair computers, smartphones and professional audio equipment with affordable prices, a custom designed online tracking system, and fast turnaround time.\\nWe not only meet but exceed our customer’s expectations. We offer a full range of repair services and technical support including in-home or on-site business services including wireless networking, network printer setup, on-site computer support & outcalls in the NYC area.\\n\\n### Why repair instead of replace?\\n\\nRepairs are less costly than replacing, better for the environment, less time consuming (no reinstalling software and migrating your important files) and much less aggravating. The premature disposal of easily repairable electronic equipment adds even more toxic waste to landfills. So go green _and_ save money by repairing your electronics at iFIX New York!\\n\\nTELL US ABOUT YOUR PROBLEM\\n\\nYour Name\\n\\nYour Number\\n\\nYour Email\\n\\nDescribe the scope of the job\\n\\nI agree to receive informational texts from **iFix** about my repair. Consent not required for purchase. Frequency may vary. Msg&data rates may apply. Reply STOP to cancel, HELP for help. Privacy Policy | Terms and Conditions\\nThank you for your message.\\n\\nIt has been sent.\\n\\n## About iFix New York\\n\\nabout-image\\n\\n#### State-of-the-art Electronics Repair in NYC\\n\\nWe’re all about top-tier electronics repair across the city. With locations in:\\n\\n* Downtown,\\n* Midtown,\\n* Upper East Side,\\n* Bay Ridge,\\n* and South Brooklyn.\\n\\n#### Why Repair Instead of Replace?\\n\\nWe offer a full range of services, including on-site business support and in-home repairs. Repairs are less costly than replacing, better for the environment, less time consuming and much less aggravating. The premature disposal of easily repairable electronic equipment adds even more toxic waste to landfills.\\n\\n1\\n\\nDIAGNOSTICS\\n\\nTo correctly estimate the time and complexity of the repair\\n\\n2\\n\\nAGREED DETAILS\\n\\nWe coordinate the details with the client and discuss the risks\\n\\n3\\n\\nREPAIR\\n\\nWe carry out high-quality repairs according to the wishes of the customer\\n\\nTELL US ABOUT YOUR PROBLEM\\n\\nYour Name\\n\\nYour Number\\n\\nYour Email\\n\\nDescribe the scope of the job\\nI agree to receive informational texts from **iFix** about my repair. Consent not required for purchase. Frequency may vary. Msg&data rates may apply. Reply STOP to cancel, HELP for help. Privacy Policy | Terms and Conditions\\n\\nThank you for your message.\\n\\nIt has been sent.\\n\\nREAL CUSTOMER TESTIMONIALS\\n\\nFAQ\\n\\nHow long will it take to repair my device?\\n\\nThe repair time will also depend on the severity of the damage. However, you can expect most repairs to be completed within a few days. We will able to give you a more accurate estimate once they have inspected your device. Do you offer a warranty on your repairs?\\n\\nWe offer a 90-day warranty on our repairs. This means that if the problem recurs within a certain period of time, we will fix it at no additional cost. Can you repair my game console's HDMI port?\\n\\nYes, we can repair your game console’s HDMI port. The HDMI port is a common point of failure on game consoles, and we are experienced in repairing this type o\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://www.gevernova.com/software/documentation/ifix/index.html\",\n      \"title\": \" | iFIX 2024 | Proficy Documentation | GE Vernova\",\n      \"publish_date\": null,\n      \"excerpts\": [\n        \"Log Console\\n\\n21ms 12:00:55 AM\\n\\nsearch:\\n\\n21ms 12:00:55 AM\\n\\nhash:\\n\\n11ms 12:00:55 AM\\n\\nonload\\n\\nSkip To Main Content\\n\\nLogo\\n\\nAccount\\n\\nSettings\\n\\n* * *\\n\\nLogout\\n\\nAll Files\\n\\n* All Files\\n\\nSubmit Search\\n\\nCreate Profile\\n\\nUsername \\\\*\\n\\nEmail Address \\\\*\\n\\nEmail Notifications\\n\\nI want to receive an email when...\\n\\na reply is left to one of my comments\\n\\na comment is left on a topic that I commented on\\n\\na comment is left on any topic in the Help system\\n\\nSubmit Cancel\\n\\nAn email has been sent to verify your new profile. Please fill out all required fields before submitting your information.\\n\\nFilter:\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://www.ifixit.com/News/75533/how-ifixit-scores-repairability\",\n      \"title\": \"How Is the iFixit Repairability Score Calculated?\",\n      \"publish_date\": \"2026-06-30\",\n      \"excerpts\": [\n        \"And that’s still the core philosophy of repairability at iFixit: To be truly repairable, a device should be fixable by _anyone_ —not just the manufacturer or its “authorized” technicians. Almost everything is technically “repairable” if you can ship it to a professional repair depot, equipped with highly trained technicians, expensive custom tools, and unlimited support from the manufacturer. While that’s a nice option to have, it doesn’t help if you need a repair quickly. Or if you’re in a far-flung location, or stuck at home during a pandemic. Or you have security/privacy concerns. Or it’s just prohibitively expensive. Or the OEM stopped supporting your device. A phone may be easier to ship than a tractor, but the principle remains the same—you should be able to fix it in the field.\\n\\n## Why Repairability Scoring Matters\\n\\nRepair saves money, makes the most of our finite resources, and is better than recycling. The concept is simple enough to fit on a [poster](https://www.\\nifixit.com/Manifesto) , but its implications are profound.\\n\\nThat said: judging repair- _ability_ is complex, and most consumers don’t have the means to evaluate it for themselves before making a purchasing decision. So providing a repairability score is iFixit’s way of helping you choose more confidently when plonking down your coin.\\n\\n## What the Scores Mean\\n\\n[iFixit graphic representing a zero (out of ten) repairability score.](https://valkyrie.cdn.ifixit.com/media/2023/05/12142924/0_Repairability-Score_Drop-Shadow.png) [iFixit graphic representing a five (out of ten) repairability score.](https://valkyrie.cdn.ifixit.com/media/2023/05/12142923/5_Repairability-Score_Drop-Shadow.png) [iFixit graphic representing a perfect ten (out of ten) repairability score.](https://valkyrie.cdn.ifixit.com/media/2023/05/12142925/10_Repairability-Score_Drop-Shadow.png)\\n\\nWe assign a score for each device on a 10-point scale to represent its overall repairability:\\n\\n* **10/10** = Best in class.\\nA very repairable device, with instructions and parts to match. We love to see it.\\n* **5/10** or above is a respectable score. We try to calibrate our scorecard so that below 5/10 is about where things start to tip from “You can probably fix this yourself” to “You might wanna consider calling a pro.” At 4/10 maybe you can still fix it, but it’s tougher than it needs to be.\\n* **1/10** = Most difficult (though not necessarily impossible) to repair. Practically or economically speaking, many repairs probably aren’t viable.\\n* **0/10** usually means disassembly is catastrophically destructive or impossible. Don’t get your hopes up. You’ll probably do more breaking than fixing.\\n\\n## Scoring Breakdown\\n\\nTo calculate a score, our engineers have to fully disassemble the device and record the results, using a rubric that accounts for every action, tool, and obstacle in the process. So, there’s a lot rolled into that little number—let’s break it down.\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://www.yelp.com/biz/ifix-manhattan-2\",\n      \"title\": \"IFIX - Updated June 2026 - 442 5th Ave, Manhattan, New ...\",\n      \"publish_date\": null,\n      \"excerpts\": [\n        \"IFIX - Updated June 2026 - 442 5th Ave, Manhattan, New ...\\n10:00 am - 9:00 pm Services - Ifix Device support or repair (914) 563-3331 Call Now. Simple Mac is your one-stop shop for all Apple Device Repairs.\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://www.cbinsights.com/company/ifix\",\n      \"title\": \"iFix - Products, Competitors, Financials, Employees, Headquarters Locations\",\n      \"publish_date\": null,\n      \"excerpts\": [\n        \"# iFix\\n\\nUnclaimed\\n\\n[ifixegypt.com](https://ifixegypt.com)\\n\\n* Overview & Products\\n* Financials\\n* People\\n* Alternatives & Competitors\\n\\n## Founded Year\\n\\n2016\\n\\n## Stage\\n\\nCorporate Minority | Alive\\n\\n## Mosaic Score\\n\\nThe Mosaic Score is an algorithm that measures the overall financial health and market potential of private companies.\\n\\n\\\\-96 points in the past 30 days\\n\\n## About iFix\\n\\niFix provides mobile device repair services in the technology sector. The company performs screen replacement, hardware troubleshooting, and resolution of software issues for mobile devices. iFix serves individual consumers requiring mobile device maintenance and repair. It was founded in 2016 and is based in New Cairo, Egypt.\\n\\n## Headquarters Location\\n\\nGround Floor, Villa 519, A Zone-South of Police Academy 5th Settlement\\n\\nNew Cairo,\\n\\nEgypt\\n\\nLoading...\\n\\nLoading...\\n\\n## Expert Collections containing iFix\\nExpert Collections are analyst-curated lists that highlight the companies you need to know in the most important technology spaces.\\n\\niFix is included in **1 Expert Collection,** including **On-Demand** .\\n\\nO\\n\\n# On-Demand\\n\\n1,244 items\\n\\nLearn more by requesting a demo\\n\\n## iFix Patents\\n\\niFix has filed 1 patent.\\n\\nView Patents Chart\\n\\n|Application Date |Grant Date |Title |Related Topics |Status |\\n| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |\\n|8/7/2019 |12/24/2024 |[Platelet lysate compositions and uses thereof](https://data.uspto.gov/patent-file-wrapper/search/details/17265936/application-data) |Diseases of the eye and adnexa, Coagulation system, Disorders of sclera and cornea, Eye surgery, Clusters of differentiation |Grant |\\n\\n|Application Date |8/7/2019 |\\n| --- | --- |\\n|Grant Date |12/24/2024 |\\n|Title |[Platelet lysate compositions and uses thereof](https://data.uspto.gov/patent-file-wrapper/search/details/17265936/application-data) |\\n|Related Topics |Diseases of the eye and adnexa, Coagulation system, Disorders of sclera and cornea, Eye surgery, Clusters of differentiation |\\n|Status |Grant |\\n\\nLearn more by requesting a demo\\n\\n## Latest iFix News\\n\\n[Ifix Plans To Expand Its Electronic Device Maintenance Services To Kenya, Nigeria, And Ghana... ...](https://menafn.com/1107837455/Ifix-Plans-To-Expand-Its-Electronic-Device-Maintenance-Services-To-Kenya-Nigeria-And-Ghana)\\n\\nFeb 12, 2024\\n\\n( MENAFN - Daily News Egypt)iFix, a leading Egyptian company that specialises in electronic device maintenance, is looking to expand its operations to three African countries: Kenya, Nigeria, and Ghana soon. The company aims to diversify its income sources in foreign currency and address the gap in authorized repair and maintenance services for a large segment of consumers on the African continent. Amna Najm, the CEO of iFix, stated that the company started its operations in 2015.\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://www.yelp.com/biz/ifixes-device-repair-plainview-3\",\n      \"title\": \"IFIXES DEVICE REPAIR - Updated February 2026 - 16 Photos - 2311 W 5th St, Plainview, Texas - IT Services & Computer Repair - Phone Number - Yelp\",\n      \"publish_date\": null,\n      \"excerpts\": [\n        \"Back to Search\\n\\nYelp\\n\\n# Ifixes Device Repair\\n\\nClaimed IT Services & Computer Repair , Electronics Repair\\n\\nClosed 10:00 AM - 2:00 PM\\n\\nSee hours\\n\\nWrite a review\\n\\nAdd photos/videos\\n\\nShare\\n\\nSave\\n\\nDo you recommend this business?\\n\\nYes\\n\\nNo\\n\\nMaybe\\n\\n## Photos & videos\\n\\nSee all 16 photos\\n\\nAdd photo\\n\\n#### You Might Also Consider\\n\\nSponsored\\n\\nMetro by T-Mobile\\n\\n**0\\\\.5 miles** away from Ifixes Device Repair\\n\\nin Electronics, Telecommunications, Mobile Phones\\n\\nT-Mobile\\n\\n5\\\\.0 (4 reviews)\\n\\n**0\\\\.7 miles** away from Ifixes Device Repair\\n\\nRam Z. said \\\"My wife and I had the absolute best experience in this store. The staff was very helpful and patient when answering our questions. Our experience couldn't have gone better. Thank you!\\\" read more\\n\\nin Telecommunications, Mobile Phones, Electronics\\n\\n## About the Business\\n\\nCome see us here at IDR Ifixes Device Repair Plainview for fast and affordable prices on Cell Phone,  \\nTablet, Computer Repairs, Accessories and More.\\nIfixes Device Repair since late 2020, repairing  \\ndevices in Plainview and surrounding areas since 2010, locally owned and family owned. We offer… …\\n\\nRead more\\n\\n## Location & Hours\\n\\nSuggest an edit\\n\\n2311 W 5th St\\n\\nPlainview, TX 79072\\n\\nServing Plainview Area\\n\\nGet directions\\n\\n|Mon |* 10:00 AM - 2:00 PM |Closed now |\\n| --- | --- | --- |\\n|Tue |* 10:00 AM - 5:30 PM | |\\n|Wed |* 10:00 AM - 4:00 PM | |\\n|Thu |* 10:00 AM - 5:30 PM | |\\n|Fri |* 10:00 AM - 5:30 PM | |\\n|Sat |* 10:00 AM - 2:00 PM | |\\n|Sun |* Closed | |\\n\\n## Amenities and More\\n\\nAccepts credit cards\\n\\n## Ask the Community\\n\\nAsk a question\\n\\nYelp users haven’t asked any questions yet about Ifixes Device Repair .\\n\\n## People also searched for\\n\\nMobile Phone Repair Gaming Console Repair Apple Computer Repair Apple Watch Repair Iphone Screen Repair Hp Laptop Repair\\n\\n## Recommended Reviews\\n\\nYour trust is our priority, so businesses can't pay to alter or remove their reviews. [Learn more about reviews.](https://www.yelp.\\ncom/reviews-trust-link-tree?l=en_US)\\n\\nUsername\\n\\nLocation\\n\\n0\\n\\n0\\n\\n0\\n\\nChoose a star rating on a scale of 1 to 5\\n\\n* 1 star rating\\n  \\n  Not good\\n* 2 star rating\\n  \\n  Could’ve been better\\n* 3 star rating\\n  \\n  OK\\n* 4 star rating\\n  \\n  Good\\n* 5 star rating\\n  \\n  Great\\n\\nSelect your rating\\n\\nHey there trendsetter! You could be the first review for Ifixes Device Repair\\n\\nYelp Sort\\n\\nFilter by rating\\n\\nSearch reviews\\n\\nSearch reviews\\n\\n*\\n\\n3 reviews that are not currently recommended\\n\\nBusiness website\\n\\nifixesdevicerepair.com\\n\\nPhone number\\n\\n(806) 213-0081\\n\\nGet Directions\\n\\n2311 W 5th St Plainview, TX 79072\\n\\nSuggest an edit\\n\\n## People Also Viewed\\n\\nAlmost Free Bail Bonds\\n\\n1\\n\\nBail Bondsmen, Notaries\\n\\nEpic Computer Solutions\\n\\nIT Services & Computer Repair, Computers\\n\\nG&G Metalworks\\n\\nMetal Fabricators, Machine Shops\\n\\nOswald Printing & Office Supply\\n\\nOffice Equipment, Printing Services\\n\\nDouglas Telecom\\n\\nTelecommunications\\n\\nRia Telecommunications\\n\\nTelecommunications\\n\\nEmmanuel Mobile Truck and Trailer Repair\\n\\n1\\n\\n...\\n\\nIf you do not allow these cookies, you will experience less targeted advertising, but you will still see ads.\\n\\nCookies Details\\n\\n### Cookie List\\n\\nClear\\n\\n* checkbox label label\\n\\nApply Cancel\\n\\nConsent Leg.Interest\\n\\ncheckbox label label\\n\\ncheckbox label label\\n\\ncheckbox label label\\n\\nAccept only essential cookies Save preferences\\n\\n[](https://www.onetrust.com/products/cookie-consent/)\"\n      ]\n    }\n  ],\n  \"warnings\": null,\n  \"usage\": [\n    {\n      \"name\": \"sku_search\",\n      \"count\": 1\n    }\n  ],\n  \"session_id\": \"ses_0d4353da3ffeu8ZYFtrkmQX48u\"\n}",
